ty of motifs, and have a plain finish. Each will come with a PPT!! rag. I do have a handful of unstamped hooks too if anyone wants to request them, as well as a few lefties.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Titanium Ragman Hooks will run $55 plus shipping and the link is below. Thanks for stopping by on this MLK holiday and have a great weeke ahead! &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All gone for now, thank you so much!&amp;nbsp; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;form action=&quot;https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr&quot; method=&quot;post&quot; target=&quot;_top&quot;&gt;
